      "fields": {
        "summary": "attdef：插入块时，块的属性标记排序错乱",
        "issuetype": {
          "self": "https://jira.zwcad.com/rest/api/2/issuetype/10309",
          "id": "10309",
          "description": "A problem which impairs or prevents the functions of the product.",
          "iconUrl": "https://jira.zwcad.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10303&avatarType=issuetype",
          "name": "缺陷",
          "subtask": false,
          "avatarId": 10303
        },
        "created": "2025-11-12T15:13:57.000+0800",
        "description": "h3. 复现步骤:\r\n\r\n在ZWCAD 2024 2.2，ZWCAD 2025 2.1，或ZWCAD 2026 1.1中使用INSERT插入块\r\n\r\n选择插入附件任意文件\r\n!image-2025-10-21-10-00-16-676.png!\r\n\r\n \r\nh3. 实际结果:\r\n\r\n插入附件图块后，快中的属性排列顺序错乱\r\n!image-2025-10-21-10-00-45-724.png!\r\nh3. 期望结果:\r\n\r\n快属性排列正常，同ZWCAD 2024/2025效果\r\n!image-2025-10-21-10-01-24-340.png!\r\n\r\nps：acad的属性排列顺序与原ZWCAD 2024/2025效果也一致",
